'''柔佛名人博物馆'''（{{lang-ms|Muzium Tokoh Johor}}）为[[柔佛州|柔佛州]]的博物馆，为[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]现任[[外交部长|外交部长]]的[[希沙慕丁|拿督斯里希沙慕丁]]、[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]第三任[[首相|首相]]的[[侯赛因·奥恩|敦胡先翁]]及[[巫统|巫统]]创立者[[翁嘉化|拿督斯里翁嘉化]]的先辈，拿督嘉化穆罕默德的官邸，现为拥有135年的博物馆。

==历史==
博物馆大楼最初建于1886年，位于当时[[英属马来亚|英属马来亚]][[新山|新山]]的微笑山（Bukit Senyum）的顶部，建立初期俯视着新山全景，甚至能遥望隔着[[柔佛海峡|柔佛海峡]]的另一岸[[新加坡|新加坡]][[兀兰|兀兰]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.themalaymailonline.com/travel/article/how-to-spend-24-hours-in-heritage-rich-johor-bahru#c6swSqHF5WChCL8X.97|date=1/10/2015|title=How to spend 24 hours in heritage-rich Johor Baru|publisher=Malay Mail Online|access-date=11/1/2018|archive-date=2018-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180212092144/http://www.themalaymailonline.com/travel/article/how-to-spend-24-hours-in-heritage-rich-johor-bahru#c6swSqHF5WChCL8X.97|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nst.com.my/lifestyle/sunday-vibes/2017/08/273282/colours-nation|date=2017-08-27|first=Kerry-Ann|last=Augustin|title=Colours of a nation|publisher=New Straits Times|access-date=2018-07-27|archive-date=2018-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180727085103/https://www.nst.com.my/lifestyle/sunday-vibes/2017/08/273282/colours-nation|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first1=Helen|last1=Gray|date=12/7/2018|url=https://www.theiskandarian.com/news/partly-lost-in-translation/|title=Partly Lost in Translation|publisher=The Iskandarian|access-date=2020-06-24|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920194412/https://www.theiskandarian.com/news/partly-lost-in-translation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

柔佛名人博物馆是自1866年[[柔佛大皇宫|柔佛大皇宫]]建立以来的另一座历史殖民建筑，曾成为[[柔佛|柔佛]]第一任部长嘉化穆罕默德的房屋。

==建筑==

该博物馆位于柔佛州第一任首席部长嘉化·穆罕默德（Muhammad Jafaar）的官邸拿督贾法尔大厦（Bangunan Dato' Jaafar）中。该建筑建在Bukit Senyum的100公顷土地上。<ref>{{cite web|last=Noraslindaar|date=2020-09-29|url=https://people.utm.my/noraslindaar/2020/09/29/muzium-tokoh-johor/|title=Figure Museum Johor|trans-title=Muzium Tokoh Johor|language=ms|work=Universiti Teknologi Malaysia|access-date=2021-01-22|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128214811/https://people.utm.my/noraslindaar/2020/09/29/muzium-tokoh-johor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

该建筑类似于[[英国|英国]]的英国王室建筑[[哈德威克厅|哈德威克厅]]（Hardwick Hall）。该建筑由三层楼和每个角落的四座塔组成。<ref name="ywj">{{cite web|url=http://www.ywj.gov.my/muzium-tokoh-johor/|work=Yayasan Warisan Johor|title=Muzium Tokoh Johor|access-date=2016-10-20|language=ms|archive-date=2019-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190123224736/http://www.ywj.gov.my/muzium-tokoh-johor/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==展览==
博物馆展示了柔佛和[[柔佛苏丹国|柔佛苏丹国]]的历史。它还定期举办有关柔佛州著名人物的临时展览。<ref>{{cite news|author=BERNAMA|date=2019-09-18|url=https://www.sinarharian.com.my/article/48271/EDISI/Johor/Sejarah-tokoh-sastera-budaya-dipamer-di-Muzium-Tokoh|title=Sejarah tokoh sastera, budaya dipamer di Muzium Tokoh|trans-title=History, Culture of Literature Figures Showcased at Figure Museum|language=ms|access-date=2021-01-22|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128105004/https://www.sinarharian.com.my/article/48271/EDISI/Johor/Sejarah-tokoh-sastera-budaya-dipamer-di-Muzium-Tokoh|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|date=2019-09-18|url=https://www.johorkini.my/pameran-tokoh-sastera-johor-shaharom-husain-di-muzium-tokoh-johor/|title=Pameran Tokoh Sastera Johor, Shaharom Husain di Muzium Tokoh Johor|trans-title=Shaharom Husain, Johor's Literature Figure Exhibition in Figure Museum Johor|language=ms|access-date=2021-01-22|archive-date=2021-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129100014/https://www.johorkini.my/pameran-tokoh-sastera-johor-shaharom-husain-di-muzium-tokoh-johor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

